            <section ID="id_link_07eaac2c-60b0-578b-e054-00144ff8d46c">
               <id root="07eaac2c-60b1-578b-e054-00144ff8d46c"/>
               <code code="34089-3" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DESCRIPTION SECTION"/>
               <title>
                  <content styleCode="bold">DESCRIPTION </content>
               </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Releevia Patch contains capsaicin and menthol in a localized dermal delivery system. The capsaicin in Releevia is a synthetic equivalent of the naturally occurring compound found in chili peppers. Capsaicin is soluble in alcohol, acetone, and ethyl acetate and very slightly soluble in water. The menthol is slightly soluble in water.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Releevia is a single-use patch stored in a foil pouch. Each Releevia patch is 8.3 cm x 12.5 cm (104 cm 
  <sup>2</sup>) and consists of a polyester backing film coated with a drug-containing silicone adhesive mixture, and covered with a removable polyester release liner.
 </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>The empirical formula for capsaicin is C 
  <sub>18</sub>H 
  <sub>27</sub>NO 
  <sub>3</sub>, with a molecular weight of 305.42. The chemical compound capsaicin [(E)-8-methyl-N-vanillyl-6-nonenamide] is an activating ligand for transient receptor potential vanilloid 1 receptor (TRPV1) and it has the following structure:
 </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <renderMultiMedia referencedObject="MM1"/>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>The empirical formula for menthol is C 
  <sub>10</sub>H 
  <sub>20</sub>O, with a molecular weight of 156.27. The chemical compound menthol [(1 
  <content styleCode="italics">R</content>,2 
  <content styleCode="italics">S</content>,5 
  <content styleCode="italics">R</content>)-2-isopropyl-5-methylcyclohexanol ] is an activating ligand for transient receptor potential cation channel subfamily M member 8 (TRPM8). It has the following structure:
 </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <renderMultiMedia referencedObject="MM2"/>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Each Releevia Patch contains 0.0375% capsaicin (0.0375 grams of capsaicin per patch) and 5.00% menthol (5 grams of menthol per patch). The Releevia patch contains the following inactive ingredients: Aloe Barbadensis Leaf (Aloe Vera Gel) Juice, Diazolidinyl Urea, EDTA Disodiumm Salt, Glycerin, Iodoproynyl Butylcabamate, Methylparaben, Polysorbate 80, Propylparaben, Sodium Polyacrylate, and Water.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20141117"/>
